Step 1  
Clone git nya

Step 2 Buat Dockerfile  
Dockerfile  
![][image1]

| \# Dockerfile FROM php:8.1-fpm \# Install basic dependencies RUN apt-get update && apt-get install \-y \\     unzip \\     git \\     && apt-get clean && rm \-rf /var/lib/apt/lists/\* \# Set working directory WORKDIR /var/www \# Copy application files COPY . . \# Install Composer RUN curl \-sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php \-- \--install-dir=/usr/local/bin \--filename=composer \# Install Laravel dependencies RUN composer install  |
| :---- |

Step 3 Buat file `docker-compose.yml`  
docker-compose.yml  
![][image2]

| version: '3.8' services:   app:     build:       context: .       dockerfile: Dockerfile     volumes:       \- .:/var/www     expose:       \- "9000"  \# Meng-expose port 9000 untuk komunikasi dengan Nginx     depends\_on:       \- db   nginx:     image: nginx:alpine     volumes:       \- .:/var/www  \# Mount folder aplikasi Laravel       \- ./nginx/default.conf:/etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf  \# Mount konfigurasi Nginx     ports:       \- "8000:80"  \# Arahkan port 8000 di host ke port 80 di container Nginx     depends\_on:       \- app   db:     image: mysql:5.7     environment:       MYSQL\_ROOT\_PASSWORD: root       MYSQL\_DATABASE: laravel       MYSQL\_USER: user       MYSQL\_PASSWORD: password     ports:       \- "3307:3307"  |
| :---- |

Step 4 Siapkan File `.env`  
`cp .env.example .env`  
`DB_CONNECTION=mysql`   
`DB_HOST=db DB_PORT=3306`   
`DB_DATABASE=laravel`   
`DB_USERNAME=user`   
`DB_PASSWORD=password`

Step 5 Atur file nginx .conf nya  
Default.conf  
![][image3]

| server {     listen 80;     server\_name localhost;     root /var/www/public;  \# Pastikan ini mengarah ke folder public Laravel     index index.php index.html index.htm;     location / {         try\_files $uri $uri/ /index.php?$query\_string;     }     location \~ \\.php$ {         include fastcgi\_params;         fastcgi\_param SCRIPT\_FILENAME $document\_root$fastcgi\_script\_name;         fastcgi\_pass app:9000;  \# Nama service PHP di docker-compose.yml     } }  |
| :---- |

Step 6 Build Image dengan perintah  ‘docker-compose up \-d \--build’

![][image4]

Step 7 Periksa Image dan container nya apakah sudah run

Container ls  
![][image5]

Docker images  
![][image6]

Step 8 , jika sudah jalan lakukan perintah berikut ‘docker exec \-it bds-devops-project-tugas-9\_app\_1 bash’

Step 9, Jalankan Perintah ‘php artisan migrate’

Step 10, cek di browser apakah sudah jalan

Localhost:8000  
![][image7]
